      "text": [
        " : «يُجْزِيكَ أَنْ تَأْخُذَ حَصَى اَلْجِمَارِ مِنَ اَلْحَرَمِ كُلِّهِ إِلاَّ مِنَ اَلْمَسْجِدِ اَلْحَرَامِ وَ مَسْجِدِ اَلْخَيْفِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2997 - Hanan ibn Sadeer narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"It is sufficient for you to take the pebbles for the Jamarat from anywhere within the boundaries of the Haram, except from the Sacred Mosque (Masjid al-Haram) and Masjid al-Khayf.\""
        ]
      }
